name: AnemiaForErythropoesisSimulatingAgents
title: Anemia for Erythropoesis Simulating Agents
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Codes indicating a diagnosis of anemia for which erythropoesis stimulating agents would be appropriate.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Codes for anemia, including aplastic and other bone marrow failure syndromes),(Exclusion Criteria: * Nutritional anemias (e.g., iron, folate, B12), * hemolytic anemias, * anemia due to enzyme disorders *post-hemorrhagic anemia)
